"Complete FEM Workflow — Symbolic + Numeric

"1. Symbolic: Shape Functions
#deq N_1 = 1 - ξ
#deq N_2 = ξ
#sym diff(1-t; t)
#sym diff(t; t)
#deq B = [-1/L; 1/L]

"2. Geometry (pure numeric, kN and m)
'E=200000000 kN/m², A=0.005 m², L₁=3m, L₂=4m
E_v = 200000000
A_v = 0.005
L_1 = 3
L_2 = 4

"3. Element Stiffness
'k₁ = EA/L₁:
k_1 = E_v*A_v/L_1
K_1 = k_1*[1; -1 | -1; 1]
'k₂ = EA/L₂:
k_2 = E_v*A_v/L_2
K_2 = k_2*[1; -1 | -1; 1]

"4. Assembly (node 1 fixed → 2 DOF)
k1_22 = K_1.(2;2)
k2_11 = K_2.(1;1)
k2_12 = K_2.(1;2)
k2_22 = K_2.(2;2)
K_R = [k1_22 + k2_11; k2_12 | k2_12; k2_22]
F_R = [0; 100]

"5. Solve
u_R = lsolve(K_R; F_R)
'u₂ (mm):
u_R.(1)*1000
'u₃ (mm):
u_R.(2)*1000

"6. Symbolic
#deq K_axial = E*A/L*[1; -1 | -1; 1]
#sym det(k1_22 + k2_11; k2_12; k2_12; k2_22)
#sym eigen(k1_22 + k2_11; k2_12; k2_12; k2_22)
